<h3>
    Neefun Swim 简介 (Introduction to Neefun Swim)：
</h3>
<div>
    <p>
        Neefun 游泳队是由一些热心于儿童教育的在校学生的家长发起组织。
        游泳队建立的宗旨不在于争夺名次，而是通过正确的游泳姿势，适当提高体能，
        通过游泳这一过程发展团队合作精神，树立积极向上的人生观，使游泳成为终身受用的运动。
    </p>
    <p>
        Neefun Swim is launched by a team of passionate parents and an energetic
        coach of strong backgrounds working with children.
        We believe swimming will not only help children build strong bodies,
        but also help them build strong minds.  Join Neefun Swim, have a fun and rewarding experience,
        and gain a positive personality.
    </p>

    <h4>主教练Joey Xiong (Head Coach)</h4>
    <p>
       主教练Joey Xiong前中国四川省游泳队，海军游泳集训队队员。师从中国第一个亚洲男子蛙王金浦。在海军队，与世界短泳冠军宁泽涛同项目训练。美国游泳协会教练员，美国幼儿教育专业。
    </p>
    <p>
        Neefun swim head coach Joey Xiong is experienced in teaching children
        at different levels and ages. She majors in children's education and
        loves to work with children. coach Joey is US Swimming certified and a
        former member of Sichuan Professional Swim Team in China.
    </p>

    <h4>Coach Elsa</h4>
    <p>
        Elsa在中国学会游泳,后来高中去了澳大利亚,在澳大利亚又学了一段时间游泳,转学去了加拿大，现在在美国。 她有丰富的教小孩的经验，中英文都非常流利。 
    </p>
    <p>
        Elsa learned swimming in China and continued learning swimming in Australia and Canada 
        before moved to the US. She has extensive experience teaching children and is fluent in both English and Chinese.
    </p>
</div>

